    <p>
      EscapeCalifornia.com is a neutral, practical resource for people and small businesses
      who are curious about moving out of California.
    </p>

    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Offer information and checklists to evaluate a move.</li>
      <li>Help you think through taxes, cost of living, and quality-of-life tradeoffs.</li>
      <li>Connect you with professionals who can assist (in later versions).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What we don’t do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We’re not a law firm or financial advisor.</li>
      <li>We don’t give individualized legal or tax advice.</li>
      <li>We don’t do political advocacy – we focus on practical next steps.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      That said, we know it can feel like a game of “escape the boss level” just to
      keep your sanity and savings. This site keeps the tone light while staying useful.
    </p>
  </main>
